          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啦，那姬千岁将你召进府去，但不知为了何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无非是教习拳棒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既是教习拳棒，儿为何眼中落泪呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿不曾落泪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你脸上泪痕未干，还敢强辩！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲不必动怒。只因孩儿不愿为官，愿在家中侍奉母亲。是儿进退两难，故而"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "落泪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啦，为娘倒明白了。想必是那姬千岁将儿召进府去，有什么大事相托。你看"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为娘年迈，不肯前去，你道是也不是？"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既被母亲道破，孩儿不敢隐瞒。儿对母亲实说了罢！那姬千岁，将儿召进府去，"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "对儿言道：吴王姬僚为君不正，命孩儿献鱼为名，在酒席筵前，行刺那王僚！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听一言来魂下掉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "酒席筵前儿刺王僚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的儿啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "怕儿性命难脱逃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "那贼人马有多少"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "母亲不必珠泪掉，"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "孩儿言来听根苗："
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "孩儿再去立功劳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "那贼人马有多少"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲不必如此，但等母亲百年之后，儿在立功，也还不迟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但等母亲百年老"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿此言差矣。自古道：受人点水之恩，当答涌泉之报。不必挂念为娘，只管"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前去才是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想那王僚驾下，能将不少，孩儿此去，定然吉凶难定，存亡未卜。倘有不测，"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲膝下，无人尽孝，孩儿我怎能割舍？"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看为娘，桑榆暮景。想你那妻子，颇知礼仪，侍奉为娘，最是尽心。我儿只"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "管前去。为娘有言，儿且听了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "姬千岁有贤明为人有道，"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我的儿保真主莫要辞劳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "方显你尽孝心万古名标。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "自古道尽其忠难行孝道"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "谢罢了老娘亲将儿调教，"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "坐草堂听孩儿细说根苗："
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "难免那酒席筵前赴阴曹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "还未曾报娘恩养育劬劳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "此一番刺王僚凶多吉少"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "非是儿贪生命不把主保"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "遵奉母命就为孝，"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "奉养高堂食饱勤劳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "为娘方得喜眉梢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "此一番刺王僚凶多吉少"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "非是儿贪生命不把主保"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啦，如今天下刀兵四起。儿为文官则须尽忠，儿为武将则须报效，你休要迟"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "迟，快些去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快些前去休迟了"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快些前去休迟了"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "多谢母亲将儿教，"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不由专诸泪双抛！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "快些前去休迟了"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿的娘啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快些前去休迟了"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "但愿老娘年寿高。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "今生难以行孝道"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "拜别母亲出门道"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啦，儿啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "难舍难离痛难消。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "尽忠哪有行孝好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老娘亲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "孩儿不愿凌烟标。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊儿啦，你为何去而复转？"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非是孩儿去而复转。只因母亲年迈，无人侍奉，孩儿放心不下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗！你既受姬千岁重礼相托，你不肯前去，你就为不忠不孝之人，为娘就要打！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打死孩儿，儿也是不去的了哇……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（专诸哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听儿言来心焦躁，"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "思量辗转无有计一条。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "把老身的良言付与了波涛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "岂不是耽误了儿立功劳？"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "就死黄泉也逍遥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "无夫就当从儿曹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老身就当赴阴朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "娘有一言听根苗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啦。你不愿尽忠，情愿尽孝，此话当真？"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的儿生来性情傲"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿若是全孝道"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老身今日花甲老"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有夫从夫妇之道"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿尽忠把国保"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回头便把专诸叫"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿焉敢道谎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为娘与你讲了半日，舌干口燥，取碗水来，为娘一用。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。待孩儿厨下取来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉，为娘要吃涧下清泉之水。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿村外去取。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（专诸挑桶下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀且住！趁此时我儿不在家中，待我行个自尽了罢啊……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（专母哭，拴套。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "对白绫不由我哈哈大笑！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你成就我节烈万古名标。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的儿啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专母",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "为儿立功赴阴曹。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（专母上吊。专诸上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "适才取水心惊跳，"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "回到家中奉年高。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（专诸看，甩桶。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "见母亲行自尽心如刀绞，"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "可叹娘为姣儿受尽煎熬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "哭一声老娘亲，哦呀儿的娘啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "见了贤妻说根苗。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（专妻上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "专妻",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "忽听前堂一声吵，"
        },
        {
          "character": "专妻",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "见了婆母问根苗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿夫为何这等模样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀妻呀！母亲命丈夫帮助姬光千岁刺王僚，为丈夫言道，母亲百年之后，方"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "能前去；母亲命我村外取水，谁知母亲自尽了哇……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（专诸哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "专妻",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喂呀……"
        },
        {
          "character": "专妻",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "媳妇村外种田稻，"
        },
        {
          "character": "专妻",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不想婆婆赴阴曹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专妻",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "婆母啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专妻",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "珠泪滚滚锁眉梢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专妻",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "哭一声婆母命丧了"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤妻将母亲尸首，停放灵床之上，我还要守孝百日。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊夫哇！母亲一死，遗言在耳，你还不前去立功？家中之事，均有为妻料理。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若不去，看母亲拐杖在此！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妻呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "贤妻不必泪垂掉，"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "丈夫言来听根苗："
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "埋葬吉地要安牢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "清明佳节把纸烧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "还要贤妻好教调。"
        },
        {
          "character": "专诸",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "行刺王僚美名标。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（专诸下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "专妻",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "见儿夫上了阳关道，"
        }
